item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Liam Gallagher & John Squire - "Liam Gallagher & John Squire" (Album)
item.description:
At the time of writing this, the album isn't out yet. It comes out in 12 hours, 44 minutes, and 30 seconds... it offically releases 1st of March, or midnight for me.
Liam Gallgher from Oasis and John Squire from The Stone Roses come together for a 10-track collab album.



When it comes out, I'd love to have this in FLAC please.
Here's the qobuz for any reference: https://www.qobuz.com/ca-en/album/l...uire-liam-gallagher-john-squire/h84j9s2cvwk7a

Many thanks!
